      "line": 7,
      "message": "The code you see here (and all that lives in ansible/test scope) is just test framework setup and hence it does not matter whether it's idempotent or not so no use adding such conditions. Molecule has a test env state management so it wouldn't even allow running \"prepare\" step twice without running \"cleanup\" (rollbacks test env to initial step, we don't use it) first.",
